+ * \def MBEDTLS_SHA1_USE_X86_SHA_NI_IF_PRESENT
+ *
+ * Enable acceleration of the SHA-1 cryptographic hash algorithm
+ * with the x86/x64 SHA extensions (SHA-NI) if they are available at runtime.
+ * If not, the library will fall back to the C implementation.
+ *
+ * \note If MBEDTLS_SHA1_USE_X86_SHA_NI_IF_PRESENT is defined when building
